"{\n  \"text\": \"Hey everybody, I'm out here in Neadville, Texas, on the plot of land we are looking to regenerate, and I'm going to do a quick video about the soil conditions here. If you'll look at the barren soil and the way the water puddles up, it is highly hydrophobic, which means the water does not want to settle in, it just uh sits on top. And then if you'll see that basically there's a little bit of scrub brush and some of the more hardy plants that can dig into this, but for the most part, there's no ground covering. I'd say about 60% of the ground is just open and bare. And what happened here is that there was a chemical fertilizer application for many years. About 10 years ago, they stopped it, and then it's been overgrazed uh with I probably a half dozen horses in 14 acres, or maybe more close to a dozen, and it's just really degraded the ground. And this is what we're gonna try to fix up with our regenerative gardening project. Anyway, thanks y'all.\",\n  \"sentences\": [\n    {\n      \"text\": \" Hey everybody, I'm out here in Neadville, Texas, on the plot of land we are looking to regenerate, and I'm going to do a quick video about the soil conditions here.\",\n      \"start\": 1.2,\n      \"end\": 10.4,\n      \"duration\": 9.2,\n      \"confidence\": 0.993,\n      \"tokens\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \" He\",\n          \"start\": 1.2,\n          \"end\": 1.44,\n          \"duration\": 0.24,\n          \"confidence\": 0.996\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"y\",\n          \"start\": 1.44,\n          \"end\": 1.6,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" ever\",\n          \"start\": 1.68,\n          \"end\": 1.76,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"yb\",\n          \"start\": 1.76,\n          \"end\": 1.92,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n     